description: Application pursuant to s73 for further variation of condition 13 (approved drawing numbers) to enable minor material amendment to planning permission granted 30 March 2012 (ref: 2011/2089, as amended) for demolition of the existing buildings, erection of two new buildings of up to 17-storeys and 15-storeys in height to provide 456 residential units (reduced by subsequent amendments to 448 dwellings) and 1,257sqm of commercial floor area comprising of office (B1 and A2), retail (A1) and caf/restaurant (A3) uses, together with new pedestrian link and vehicular access, basement car and cycle parking, landscaping, excavation works and servicing. Amendment relates to the relocation of affordable business unit and the creation of two duplex residential apartments to Block L at ground and basement level.
